_embedded.promptText: Test Question Grid
How often do you have a drink containing alcohol?
Overall, what is the number of units you take per week?
How many drinks containing alcohol do you have on a typical day when you are drinking?
How often do you have six or more drinks on one occasion?
How often during the last year, have you found that you were not able to stop drinking once you had started?
How often during the last year have you failed to do what was normally expected of you because of drinking?
How often during the last year have you needed a first drink in the morning to get yourself going after a heavy drinking session?
How often during the last year have you had a feeling ofÂ guilt or remorse after drinking?
How often during the last year have you been unable to remember what happened the night before because of your drinking?
How many days of at least 30 minutes of activity have you had in the last 7 days?
What do you most usually smoke?
Have you or someone else been injured because of your drinking?
Has a relative, friend, doctor or other health care worker been concerned about your drinking or suggested you cut down?
How many do you smoke per day?
How long have you been a smoker? (In years)
Have you a potential Quit Date?
Does your work involve vigorous-intensity activity that causes large increases in breathing or heart rate for at least 10 minutes continuously?
Are you using products to assist? (e.g., nicotine patches, gum, lozenges)
Do you walk or use a bicycle for at least 10 minutes continuously to get to and from places?
In a typical week, on how many days do you do vigorous-intensity sports, fitness or recreational activity?
In a typical week, on how many days do you do moderate-intensity sports, fitness or recreational activity that can cause a SMALL increase in breathing or heart rate?
In a typical week, how many days do you do vigorous-intensity activities as part of your work?
What, if any, activities are you currently using to attempt weight loss?
Describe "Other" activities currently using for weight loss:
For what length of time would you be interested in pursuing a weight loss program? (In months)
